# Cursor Rules for c7e/controller

## Repository Overview
This repository contains a Starknet smart contract wallet implementation with TypeScript/JavaScript packages for web and Node.js integration.

## Development Guidelines
- Follow TypeScript best practices with proper typing
- Use camelCase for variables/functions, PascalCase for components/types
- Organize imports with external dependencies first, then internal
- Prefix React hooks with "use"
- Test new functionality and update storybook snapshots when changing UI

## Common Commands
- Build: `pnpm build`
- Lint: `pnpm lint`
- Format: `pnpm format`
- Test: `pnpm test`
- Storybook: `pnpm storybook`

## Error Handling
Use custom error classes with descriptive codes and messages. Propagate errors properly through promises.